   1→//! UPnP/DLNA adapter - discovers and controls UPnP Media Renderers
   2→//!
   3→//! Uses SSDP for discovery and UPnP AV Transport service for control.
   4→//! Pure UPnP/DLNA has limited metadata support compared to OpenHome.
   5→//! Specifically, next/previous track are NOT supported by pure UPnP.
   6→
   7→use crate::adapters::handle::{AdapterHandle, RetryConfig};
   8→use crate::adapters::traits::{
   9→    AdapterCommand, AdapterCommandResponse, AdapterContext, AdapterLogic,
  10→};
  11→use crate::bus::{
  12→    BusEvent, PlaybackState, PrefixedZoneId, SharedBus, VolumeControl as BusVolumeControl, Zone,
  13→};
